By Adeyinka Aderibigbe  A lone accident was recorded on the inward Iyana Oworo carriage of the Third Mainland Bridge on Tuesday. The bus which may have been returning to Oshodi from Oke Arin Market on the Island was seen engulfed in fire. Though our reporter could not pick any information regarding the source of the fire, some of the goods the bus was carrying littered the scene of the accident. A police team was seen controlling traffic at the scene of the accident. The police said no lives were lost in the accident though some of the commuters sustained various injuries.  Details shortlyâ€¦